snippet.title: YOU DON'T KNOW JACK MOVIES Trailer
snippet.description: YDKJ: Movies is considered the most challenging game in the series -- are you up for the challenge? Test your movie knowledge from back when movies were movies, and movie candy didn't have high fructose corn syrup!
